note checkerboard.vrb — alternating * and space checkerboard.
note Prints * when (row + col) is even, space otherwise.

ask the user "board size?" and save to size.

row = 1.
while row <= size:
    col = 1.
    while col <= size:
        check = row + col.
        remainder = check % 2.
        if remainder == 0:
            display "*".
        else:
            display " ".
        end.
        col += 1.
    end.
    say.
    row += 1.
end.
